                    <ab>Igitur fidelium nostrorum presentium ac futurorum noverit multitudo. Quoniam
                        per <rs key="#Intercessory">interventum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory" ref="#people/4246">Tancredi cognomine de
                            Altavilla</persName> et <persName key="#Intercessory #childOf"
                            ref="#people/4248">Guilielmi</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/4247">Guilielmi Frasnelli </persName>et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory" ref="#people/4249">Ugonis de Phaida</persName>, quam
                        et ad salutem et remedium animarum <rs key="#Princeps">principum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #grandparentOf" ref="#people/3001"
                            >Richardi</persName> scilicet <rs key="#grandparentOf">avi</rs> et
                            <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3002"
                            >Iordanis</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs> nostri, et ob statu nostri principatus,
                        concedimus et confirmamus per hoc nostrum principalem scriptum omnipotenti
                        Deo et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Immunity #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> sito in <placeName ref="#places/109">Monte
                            Casino</placeName>, in quo domnus <persName key="#Abbots #Personal_rank"
                            ref="#people/2416">Oderisius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> praeest, et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3046">Sancti Arcangeli
                            Michahelis in Formis</orgName> in quo domnus <persName
                            key="#Prevosts #Personal_rank" ref="#people/4245">Sasso</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">prepositus</rs> preest, quicquid <persName
                            key="#Count #marriage" ref="#people/4250">Paldi</persName> qui fuerat
                            <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> de <placeName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#places/4545">Sexto</placeName> et <rs key="#marriage">uxore</rs>
                        sua <persName key="#marriage"><name ref="Maria">Maria</name></persName> de
                        hereditate eorum in prenominato monasterio Sancti Benedicti per <rs
                            key="#Cartula">cartulam</rs> obtulerunt, ubicumque exinde inventus
                        fuerit intro vel foras <rs key="#Cities">civitatibus</rs> vel <rs
                            key="#Castle">castellis</rs>, <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>,
                        planis, <rs key="#Rivers #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aquis</rs>
                        atque <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Forests #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">silvis</rs>, in
                        omnibus scilicet qualiter in eadem cartula offersionis continere videtur.
                        Simili modo concedimus et confirmamus in prescriptis monasteriis, <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3066">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> quae est sita in loco qui <placeName
                            ref="#places/4546">Dalfiana</placeName> vocatur, in <rs key="#Comitatus"
                            >comitatu</rs><placeName ref="#places/4062" key="#Comitatus"><geogName
                                ref="#estates/3032" key="#Comitatus"> Castello
                            maris</geogName></placeName>, prope <placeName ref="#places/4547"
                            >Rosellam</placeName> quae <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/4251">Ugo de Molinis </persName>in
                        predicto monasterio Sancti Benedicti, et monasterio Sancti Angeli, per
                        cartula offersionis dedit cum pertinentiis suis omnibus. Haec omnia predicta
                        qualiter supra prenotata sunt, Nos prephatus <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/3010">saecundus
                            Richardus</persName>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capuanus</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, in predictis monasteriis concedimus et
                        confirmamus ad possessionem et potestatem et dominationem predictis
                        monasteriis et predicti domni Oderisii abbati et domni Sassoni eorumque
                        successorum atque custodum, faciendo exinde quicquid eis placuerint. Remota
                        omni contrarietate et molestatione omnium principum successorum nostrorum,
                        vel vice principum successorum nostrorum, comitum vel vice comitum, iudicum,
                        sculdahorum, castaldeorum aliorumque omnium mortalium. Quod si quis huius
                        nostrae concessionis et confirmationis paginae in aliquo contemptor aut
                        violator esse presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">quinquaginta libras auri
                            purissimi</rs> persolvat: medietatem in predictis monasteriis et
                        predicto domno Oderisio venerabili abbati et domno Sassoni preposito
                        eorumque successoribus atque custodibus, et medietatem nostro sacro palatio.
                        Solutaque paena librarum, hoc nostrum principale scriptum cum omnibus quae
                        continet, firmum munitum atque inviolabile maneat in perpetuum. Et ut hoc
                        scriptum firmius credatur et diligentius ab omnibus observetur, manu propria
                        subscripsimus et nostri sigilli iussimus sigillari. (M) Ex iussionae
                        prephate serenissime potestatis, scripsi ego <persName key="#Writer #Judge"
                            ref="#people/3012">Quiriacus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs>. In anno dominicae incarnationis millesimo
                        nonogesimo octavo, et octavo decimo anno principatus prephati domni
                            <persName key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/3010"
                            >saecundi Richardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosi</rs> principis Capuae. Datum
                        apud <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/4000">Aversanam</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">urbem</rs> mense magio per indictionem sextam. </ab>
